{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Shopify AI Master Instructions: The Library Engagement Architecture
    Objective: Create two integrated segments at the bottom of the Library page (following the Author Bio) to facilitate institutional partnerships and curriculum immersion for the book Let There Be Fashion.
    
    Segment 1: The Shared Narrative (The Invitation)
    Purpose: To bridge the individual book purchase to a collective, institutional immersion.
    
    Layout: Full-width text immersion.
    
    Background Color: Pure White (#FFFFFF).
    
    Padding: 120px Top / 80px Bottom.
    
    Dividing Line: A subtle 1px horizontal rule (#E5E5E5) at the very top of the section.
    
    Typography & Copy:
    
    Eyebrow (Sans-Serif): "THE SHARED NARRATIVE" (11px, All Caps, 0.3em letter spacing, Color: #999).
    
    Header (Serif/Bodoni Moda): "IMMERSION & IMPACT" (32px, All Caps, 0.25em letter spacing).
    
    Body Text (Sans-Serif/Inter): > "Beyond the individual journey lies the opportunity for collective transformation. The Let There Be Fashion curriculum is designed for leadership collectives, academic institutions, and faith-based organizations seeking to move beyond theory and into the structural restoration of worth. We invite you to engage the House of Vuu to facilitate a shared narrative through group immersion and speaking engagements."
    
    Style: 18px, Line Height 1.8, Max-width: 800px, Centered. (Italicize the book title).
    
    CTA Button:
    
    Text: "INITIATE THE DIALOGUE"
    
    Style: Minimalist Ghost Button (1px solid black border, no background, 12px, Bold, All Caps).
    
    Link: Anchor to #engage-the-visionary.
    
    Segment 2: Engage the Visionary (The Action)
    Purpose: A sophisticated inquiry form that handles diverse requests (Curriculum, Speaking, Media).
    
    Layout: 50/50 Split (Image Left / Form Right).
    
    ID: engage-the-visionary
    
    Left Side (Visual Asset): * Image: Use the high-contrast B&W photo of Nancy Vuu speaking to a crowd with raised hands.
    
    Style: Full bleed to the left edge; apply a soft "fade-to-white" at the bottom to transition cleanly.
    
    Right Side (The Inquiry Form):
    
    Background Color: Pure White (#FFFFFF).
    
    Header (Serif): "Engage the Visionary" (Bodoni Moda, 28px).
    
    Intro Text: "Please entrust the details of your brief below as we review for visionary alignment and the potential for a shared narrative."
    
    Form Fields (Clean 1px borders, no shadows):
    
    Full Name & Title (Text)
    
    Organization / Media Outlet (Text)
    
    Professional Email (Email)
    
    Nature of Inquiry (Dropdown Menu):
    
    Let There Be Fashion Curriculum Immersion
    
    Speaking Engagement / Keynote
    
    Dream Academy & Foundation Partnership
    
    Global Advisory / Consultation
    
    Media & Press Inquiry
    
    The Vision (Text Area): Label as "Describe the narrative or mandate you wish for Nancy Vuu to deliver."
    
    Proposed Timeline (Date/Text)
    
    Final Submit Button:
    
    Text: "INITIATE THE DIALOGUE"
    
    Style: Solid Black Bar, White Text, All Caps, Bold.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-shared-narrative-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px 40px {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    border-top: 1px solid {{ block.settings.divider_color }};
  }

  .ai-shared-narrative__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-shared-narrative__eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_size }}px;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_spacing }}em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_color }};
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .ai-shared-narrative__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.heading_spacing }}em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-shared-narrative__body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.body_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.body_color }};
    max-width: {{ block.settings.body_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .ai-shared-narrative__body-{{ ai_gen_id }} em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .ai-shared-narrative__cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.button_border_color }};
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-shared-narrative__cta-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-shared-narrative-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.padding_top | times: 0.6 }}px 24px {{ block.settings.padding_bottom | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-shared-narrative__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-shared-narrative__body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.body_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-shared-narrative__cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-size: {{ block.settings.button_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-shared-narrative-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-shared-narrative__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.eyebrow != blank %}
      <div class="ai-shared-narrative__eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.eyebrow }}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
      <h2 class="ai-shared-narrative__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.heading }}
      </h2>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.body_text != blank %}
      <div class="ai-shared-narrative__body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.body_text }}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.cta_text != blank and block.settings.cta_link != blank %}
      <a href="{{ block.settings.cta_link }}" class="ai-shared-narrative__cta-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.cta_text }}
      </a>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>

